# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# docs-keeper runtime state (per-machine, never source) — session/capture files
# live under .docs-keeper/sessions/. Keep the committed config.json (per-repo
# settings, shared across the team).
/.docs-keeper/*
!/.docs-keeper/config.json

# Jekyll docs-site build artifacts (generated by `jekyll build` / Pages CI)
/docs/_site/
/docs/.sass-cache/
